					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This was inspired by the release of the JFK Assassination files yesterday and how funny it would be if the only conspiracy was that there wasn't one at all.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963936" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" >minmin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963936" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" >GreenWolf</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963936" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" >Taffeta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/salvagebar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1479603&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963936" alt="salvagebar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1479603)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/salvagebar" >salvagebar</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963936" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2938475&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963936" alt="Zhange" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2938475)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" >Zhange</a></span> for their feedback.</p> <p>See more of my work on my <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-arvind-desais-personnel-file">author page</a>!</p> 
